-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is the fifteenth episode of the new cartoon called *Famous Five: On the
Case*, *Famous 5: On the Case* or sometimes simply *Famous Five*. The name of
the episode is *The Case of The Bogus Banknotes*. Although these new episodes
have started airing way after the last one (S01E13), before the show started,
it was announced 26 episodes were made, so I assume this hasn't come back, and
they're just showing the rest. Enjoy! ;)
